    "Therefore, it is necessary to develop strategies that can effectively embed information on many-body interactions such as bond angles and local geometric distortions outside of nested graph networks.",
    "Second, there exists an imbalance in research and model development efforts across the fields of materials science, molecular science, and chemistry.",
    "Extending existing GNN models to broader application areas (such as spanning molecular, crystal materials, and catalysis fields) may be challenging and require further development of GNN models.",
